**No sustained drift away from the north star is found in the record; the north-star distance HOLDS STEADY across all 15 arcs, with two recurring trend-flags that are declared-and-contained rather than realized divergences.** Confidence: **high** on the no-sustained-drift call; **medium** on the two trend-flags being fully contained (both are forward/organizing-principle reads, field-4 only).

