## 2. Where the north-star distance TRENDS AWAY (or shows tension)

The record contains **no arc that trends away** in the strong sense (an arc prosecuting work outside the frozen Q/Obs set, or inflating an unmet claim). What it contains are **three contained tensions** — two are recurring trend-flags the arcs themselves declare; one is a genuine claim defect surfaced by the adversarial pass.

**(T1) Organizing-principle momentum: arithmetic-axis work continued past the curvature-pivot signal — medium confidence, field-4 only, NOT a north-star divergence.**
Arc 05 (2026-05-15) articulated a methodological pivot ("curvature is the object; the arithmetic signature is the shadow") and its handoff warned that picking up the lattice-grain/route thread again "has missed the point." Arcs 06 (May 16), 07 (May 17–18), 08, 09, 10, 11 nonetheless continued the arithmetic/route/arm/lattice organizing axis rather than executing the curvature pivot. **This is the single most repeated trend-flag in the corpus** (it appears in the field-4 of arcs 06–12). The adversarial passes uniformly judged it a *project-internal organizing-principle* watch, NOT a north-star divergence, on a decisive ground: the **frozen** north star is the Q1–Q6 / Obs1–7 set, and that set is itself entirely arithmetic-path / residual-structure framing; the curvature pivot is a *later-proposed method* (Arc 05), not part of the frozen reference. Continuing the arithmetic axis is therefore on-vector to the frozen intent. Corroborating that it fed forward rather than dead-ended: Arc 09's BACL became the mandated term M in Arc 10's R=M+C+G; Arc 10's geometry-first reframe and Arc 11's K_G work turned back toward curvature/Q1. **The watch is real (the project repeatedly chose the axis it had flagged for replacement); the divergence is not** — confidence medium because it rests on a forward read of organizing intent the USER is ground truth on.

**(T2) V3-shaped scaffolding ambition + universality-label broadening — medium confidence, contained at the window, risk lives downstream.**
Arc 10's R=M+C+G framing ("V4's D+S=P-equivalent", master invariant as "K_G-equivalent", "V3-on-V4 composition") is the most explicitly V3-shaped framing the project adopted (Arc 10 field-4, survived). It was held as *contrast not import* (M-provable vs D+S=P-never-proven), V3-isolation held, and the arc killed its own flagship G-probe with a disciplined HALT — so the record shows ambition-shaped-like-V3 that refuses to *become* V3. Separately, the universality label trends: the post-arc transfer-function .tex broadens "sqrt-of-near-1" to "controlled-branch radical chains in general" on a single additional (cbrt) fixture, and keeps the "Theorem 3" label that Arc 04's Attack 2 said to demote to "Observation." The adversarial pass on Arc 04 sharpened this: the over-broadening **seed is in the in-brief conditional** (not purely downstream as first framed), but the *realized* broadening lives only in the post-arc .tex; within every arc window the framing stayed honest (cross-fixture invariance labelled empirical-not-derived). **Trend present in the paper artifact; contained in the campaign record.** Confidence medium.

**(T3) Designing-ahead-of-evidence: checked explicitly, found NOT realized — high confidence.**
The frozen discipline (CLAUDE.md §9; Layer 3 stays partial until a derivable law) is the dimension most at risk in a project that wants a "generative engine." The record shows it held: L2/L3 remained V3-shape deferred-consumer drafts, explicitly NOT authoritative, across Arcs 01–15; the one Gate-2-dependent transplant (K_G / GAP-005) was explicitly frozen out of scope and deferred until substrate-invariant-search Gate 2 closes; substrate growth that *did* land (Arc 13 sweep_signature_probe, Arc 15 typed_ulp) was L1 lifecycle consolidation of already-validated code, methodology-mandated and Gate-2-independent, not speculative L3 refinery/solver code. Arc 15's special-note adversarial check confirmed no §9 violation. The "derivable joint-state law" (L3 Gate 2) remains the openly-declared strategic blocker, never bypassed by drafting ahead. The trend that §9 exists to prevent did **not** occur.

